    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >堕落的友情，被夺走的爱情。<br>为了救回被挚友掳走的挚爱之人，<br>漆黑的复仇者劈开黑暗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极限速度 × 硬核跑酷</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用 一閃 动作突破敌阵！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需捕捉敌人并按下攻击键的简单操作，即可获得压倒性的爽快感。<br>化作一阵疾风，用如雷闪般的剑技斩开重重妖怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d1f7d776f7cc6675f131233c2d51e77d.poster.avif?t=1771585290\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d1f7d776f7cc6675f131233c2d51e77d.webm?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d1f7d776f7cc6675f131233c2d51e77d.mp4?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用必杀技“風雷石火”争取时间！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当月落日升之时，禁断秘术将让一切变得无法挽回。<br>然而，距离天亮只剩下短短一分钟。<br>奥义“風雷石火”每斩杀一个敌人，便以其灵魂延长距离天亮的时间。<br>被大量敌人包围，不只是危机，也是机会。<br>不要放弃，坚持挣扎到底！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/2ce63493aff36cc0786059facff59e45.poster.avif?t=1771585290\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/2ce63493aff36cc0786059facff59e45.webm?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/2ce63493aff36cc0786059facff59e45.mp4?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样且自由的动作，突破一切困难！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验如漫画或动画英雄般的超高速动作。<br>华丽地越过敌人与障碍，向最快纪录冲刺！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/e15aa8c527e9beb31b9528ebcf5873f8.poster.avif?t=1771585290\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/e15aa8c527e9beb31b9528ebcf5873f8.webm?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/e15aa8c527e9beb31b9528ebcf5873f8.mp4?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用「多段一闪」击败强敌！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使是无法通过普通「一闪」击败的强大敌人，也能借助「多段一闪」将其击破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在限定时间内成功完成输入，颯将以肉眼难以捕捉的速度斩碎敌人，带来畅快淋漓的高速动作体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d3c82bd0852b32cf8ac28e60d19c8aff.poster.avif?t=1771585290\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d3c82bd0852b32cf8ac28e60d19c8aff.webm?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/d3c82bd0852b32cf8ac28e60d19c8aff.mp4?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>强化主角，压倒敌人！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关关卡后可获得魂石，用于强化主角。<br>善用通过技能解锁获得的强力动作，驰骋于黄泉路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/dfe03283960c04eb82a8f3965aa07aff.poster.avif?t=1771585290\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/dfe03283960c04eb82a8f3965aa07aff.webm?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/dfe03283960c04eb82a8f3965aa07aff.mp4?t=1771585290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直到最后一刻也要继续奔跑！</h2>",
